com.team23.weather.mars.dto

Class MarsWeatherResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team23.weather.mars.dto.MarsWeatherResponse

  • public class MarsWeatherResponse
extends java.lang.Object
    A MarsWeatherResponse is an object that copies the format of the JSON string representing Mars' weather. Mars' weather archive consists of both a "latest" weather forecast and an extensive "archive" of forecasts. MarsWeatherResponse is set up to only read the "latest" weather forecast. *
    Author:
    Andrew Bloch-Hansen
    See Also:
    IMarsWeatherClient, MarsWeatherClient, MarsForecast, ISerializer, Report
